      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "franさん。今日のライブ、最高でした",
      "startTime": 29.4589598736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね？　私も手応えバッチリでしたから\n今夜は気持ちよく眠れそうです",
      "startTime": 37.0048557838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.8048557838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ。今日はもう一泊するんですよね？\n場所はどこ、に……っ",
      "startTime": 43.5048557838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
