      "startTime": 62.4048557838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あー……なるほど\n確かに、ライブで激しく動きましたからね……",
      "startTime": 65.3381891172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "もう一曲歌ってたらとんでもないことに\nなってたかも……うぅ～",
      "startTime": 71.4048557838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "宿泊先に早めに行きましょう\n着替える余裕はありますか？",
      "startTime": 78.3381891172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1381891172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "それくらいなら、うぅ、はい、大丈夫、です～……\nお気遣いいただいて、すみま、せん……",
      "startTime": 87.6715224505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4715224505
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4715224505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、またこの旅館に泊まることになるなんて\nまた何か出たりしないでしょうね……うぅ……",
      "startTime": 101.3048557938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "心配なので、今日は俺も一泊します\n何かあれば言って下さい",
      "startTime": 109.7715224505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.7048557838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしなくても……あー、いえ\n確かに今日は、何か出た時のことを考えると助かります",
      "startTime": 117.9715224505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……もしこの旅館が本当に厳しかったら\nその時はなんとかしますから",
      "startTime": 126.0381891172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.4381891172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "それは……大丈夫です\nmihoとkanaは気にしてないみたいですし",
      "startTime": 132.5048567839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.9715224505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "私も、ライブの手応えはあったし……\n気分はいいんですよ",
      "startTime": 140.5381891172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.9381891172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、関係者の方から「ぜひ今度仕事を\nお願いしたい」って言ってもらえたので",
      "startTime": 147.3715224505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、メンタル面は大丈夫な訳ですね\nそれじゃあ、まずはゆっくり休んで下さい",
      "startTime": 154.2381891172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.2048557838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、そうさせてもらいます……はぁぁ～……",
      "startTime": 157.2048557838,
      "sfxList": [
