      "text": "場所が場所なんですから、急に話し掛けないで下さい\nああもう、すっかり忘れてたのに……！",
      "startTime": 189.9715224505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "すみません\nところで何を見てたんですか？",
